name: Vinyl Printed Sign
description:
- Customizable hand finished a5 vinyl sign.
- Perfect for home decoration, shop information or inspiration. 
- Weathered look - White background with black lettering 
- Up to 10 characters per line, 3 lines per sign
- Please allow up to 2 weeks for making and postage
- Simply email your word choices to MRCYSLNDN@HOTMAIL.CO.UK, wait awhile, and enjoy!

name: Hand Painted Sign
description:
- Customizable hand painted hardwood sign
- Weathered look 
- Perfect for home decoration, wedding gifts/mementos, inspiration and much more!
- Each sign is entirely hand made and unique
- Up to 20 characters per sign 
- Choice of colours - pastel pink, duck egg blue, stone grey
- Background can be painted white on request 
- Sealed for outside use
- please allow 2 weeks for painting and postage
- Simply send your wording and colour choice to MRCYSLNDN@HOTMAIL.CO.UK after ordering, wait awhile, and enjoy!
